# Mad Libs Game - If I Were President


person_in_room1 = input("Enter a person's name (in room): ")
number1 = input("Enter a number: ")
adjective1 = input("Enter an adjective: ")
color = input("Enter a color: ")
noun1 = input("Enter a noun: ")
food_plural = input("Enter a type of food (plural): ")
noun2 = input("Enter another noun: ")
verb_ing = input("Enter a verb ending in 'ing': ")
article_clothing = input("Enter an article of clothing: ")
adjective2 = input("Enter another adjective: ")
celebrity = input("Enter the name of a celebrity: ")
number2 = input("Enter another number: ")
person_in_room2 = input("Enter another person's name (in room): ")
noun3 = input("Enter another noun: ")
person_in_room3 = input("Enter yet another person's name (in room): ")
occupation = input("Enter an occupation: ")


print(f"""
         ******** IF I WERE PRESIDENT ********


My name is {person_in_room1} and I am {number1} years old. 
If I were president, I'd do a whole bunch of {adjective1} things:

1. I would drive the biggest {color} car in the country. 
   And that car would go faster than any other {noun1} in the world!

2. Everyone would eat pepperoni {food_plural} for dinner.

3. I would live in the Statue of {noun2} 
   and build a {verb_ing} pool at her feet.

4. I would wear a/an {article_clothing} on my head, 
   and everyone would say I look {adjective2} like {celebrity}.

5. School would be open only {number2} days a year.

6. I would give my friends the best jobs. 
   I would nominate {person_in_room2} to be secretary of the {noun3}, 
   and {person_in_room3} could be vice {occupation}!
""")


